This paper discusses the use of blockchain technology to combat fake news, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CR). The proposed framework also involves the use of machine learning algorithms (cs.AI) and the analysis of social networks (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential ethical and societal implications of fake news (cs.CY) and the use of deep learning algorithms (cs.DL).
